{"id":836448377,"question_id":345,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 7 months","timestamp":1667527913,"status":11,"status_display":"Wrong Answer","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/836448377/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Reverse Vowels of a String","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\n    public String reverseVowels(String s) {\n        Set<Character> set = new HashSet<>();\n        set.add('a');\n        set.add('e');\n        set.add('i');\n        set.add('o');\n        set.add('u');\n        set.add('A');\n        set.add('E');\n        set.add('I');\n        set.add('O');\n        set.add('U');\n        \n        int st=0, ed=s.length()-1;\n        \n        char[] arr = s.toCharArray();\n        \n        while(st<ed){\n            \n            if(!set.contains(s.charAt(st)))\n                st++;\n            \n             if(!set.contains(s.charAt(ed)))\n                ed--;\n            if(st<ed){\n              char temp = arr[st];\n            arr[st]= arr[ed];\n            arr[ed]=temp;\n            st++;\n            ed--;  \n            }\n            \n        }\n        \n        return new String(arr);\n        \n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"reverse-vowels-of-a-string","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
